2025-08-29 17:55:58,156 - agents - DEBUG - Обрабатываем операцию 1: {'action': 'create', 'filename': 'product_requirements.md', 'language': 'markdown', 'content': '# product_requirements.md\n### Project: E-commerce Platform MVP\n**Vision:** Create a minimal viable product (MVP) for a functional online store, enabling businesses to sell products online with essential purchase and management capabilities.\n\n**Target Audience:** Small to medium businesses (SMBs) and their customers.\n**Primary Goals:**\n1.  Allow visitors to browse products, add them to a cart, and complete a purchase.\n2.  Provide administrators with tools to manage inventory, orders, and site content.\n\n### Core Features & Modules\n1.  **Public-Facing Storefront**\n    *   **Homepage:** Display featured products, basic navigation.\n    *   **Product Catalog:** List of products, filterable by category.\n    *   **Product Detail Page (PDP):** Product image, title, description, price, "Add to Cart".\n    *   **Shopping Cart:** View added items, update quantities, remove items, see subtotal.\n    *   **Checkout Process:** Single-page for shipping details and payment.\n    *   **Order Confirmation:** Display after successful payment.\n\n2.  **User Authentication (Assumption: Simplified MVP)**\n    *   Customers can checkout as guests. User registration/login is not required for MVP but data is collected for the order.\n\n3.  **Administration Panel (Admin)**\n    *   **Authentication:** Secure login for administrators.\n    *   **Product Management (CRUD):** Create, Read, Update, Delete products (incl. name, desc, price, image, stock).\n    *   **Category Management:** Create and assign categories to products.\n    *   **Order Management:** View list of orders, see order details (items, customer info, status), update order status (e.g., Processing, Shipped).\n\n4.  **Payment Processing (Assumption: Integration with a major processor)**\n    *   Integrate with a third-party payment gateway (e.g., Stripe, PayPal).\n    *   Accept major credit/debit cards.\n    *   Process payments securely; the site will not store raw payment data.\n\n### Non-Functional Requirements\n*   **Performance:** Product catalog pages should load in under 3 seconds.\n*   **Security:** Admin panel behind login; all data transmissions (especially payment) must use HTTPS.\n*   **Usability:** Checkout process should be completable in under 2 minutes.\n*   **Browser Compatibility:** Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge (latest versions).\n\n### Out of Scope for MVP\n*   User registration profiles/wishlists.\n*   Product reviews/ratings.\n*   Advanced search with facets.\n*   Email notifications (order confirmations, shipping updates).\n*   Discount/coupon code system.\n*   Multi-currency or international shipping.\n*   Mobile app.\n\n### Assumptions\n*   A third-party payment gateway API (Stripe) will be used for processing payments.\n*   Product images will be managed via file upload in the admin panel; no external CDN or image optimization is initially required.\n*   Inventory tracking will be simple (quantity in stock); no advanced variants (e.g., sizes, colors) are needed.\n*   Shipping calculations will be flat-rate or free, not real-time carrier calculations.', 'index': 0}
