2025-08-29 17:55:58,157 - agents - DEBUG - Обрабатываем операцию 2: {'action': 'create', 'filename': 'user_stories.md', 'language': 'markdown', 'content': "# user_stories.md\n### Epic: Browse and Purchase Products\n*   **US-1:** As a Shopper, I want to view a list of available products, so that I can see what's for sale.\n*   **US-2:** As a Shopper, I want to filter products by category, so that I can quickly find relevant items.\n*   **US-3:** As a Shopper, I want to view detailed information about a single product (image, description, price), so that I can make an informed decision.\n*   **US-4:** As a Shopper, I want to add a product to my shopping cart, so that I can collect items I wish to purchase.\n*   **US-5:** As a Shopper, I want to view the contents of my shopping cart, so that I can review my selections before purchasing.\n*   **US-6:** As a Shopper, I want to change the quantity or remove items in my cart, so that I can update my order.\n*   **US-7:** As a Shopper, I want to enter my shipping and payment information on a single page, so that I can complete my purchase quickly.\n*   **US-8:** As a Shopper, I want to receive an on-screen confirmation after paying, so that I know my order was successfully placed.\n\n### Epic: Manage Store (Admin)\n*   **US-9:** As an Admin User, I want to log into a secure admin panel, so that I can manage the store.\n*   **US-10:** As an Admin User, I want to create, edit, and delete products, so that the store's inventory is up to date.\n*   **US-11:** As an Admin User, I want to upload a product image when creating/editing a product, so that customers can see the item.\n*   **US-12:** As an Admin User, I want to create and manage product categories, so that products can be organized logically.\n*   **US-13:** As an Admin User, I want to view a list of all orders, so that I can see what has been sold.\n*   **US-14:** As an Admin User, I want to view the details of a specific order (customer info, items, total), so that I can fulfill it.\n*   **US-15:** As an Admin User, I want to update the status of an order (e.g., from 'New' to 'Shipped'), so that I can track its progress.\n\n### Assumptions\n*   The Shopper is a guest user and does not need to create an account to purchase.\n*   The Admin User is a pre-configured superuser with full permissions.", 'index': 1}
